In re Mayor, Etc., of City of New York. In re Riverside Park. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Application by the corporation counsel on behalf of the mayor, etc., in the matter of the Riverside Park.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion granted, with $10 costs.
